itemDescription: promoter of education in domestic subjects (1838-1923)

wikipedia_page.main: Fanny Louise Calder (26 March 1838 – 6 June 1923) was a promoter of education in domestic subjects in Liverpool. The college that she created would in time become part of Liverpool John Moores University
